query:
SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM prices) as total_prices,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM sms_apis) as total_apis,
  (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT apiId) FROM prices) as distinct_apis_in_prices;
